257
00:17:41,227 --> 00:17:43,770
Well, I was so excited,
I opened it.

258
00:17:43,855 --> 00:17:45,689
Oh, that's okay.
What is it?

259
00:17:45,773 --> 00:17:47,566
It's about your loan.

260
