with your friends.

261
00:18:37,533 --> 00:18:39,451
VIDEO GAME:
Greetings, Starfighter.

262
00:18:44,040 --> 00:18:45,040
Greetings, Starfighter.

263
00:18:45,124 --> 00:18:47,959
You have been recruited
by the Star League to
defend the Frontier.

264
00:18:48,044 --> 00:18:49,169
