271
00:19:16,489 --> 00:19:19,491
(BEEPING)

272
00:19:29,126 --> 00:19:32,379
(AIRCRAFT DESCENDING)

273
00:19:46,435 --> 00:19:48,728
Hello. Excuse me, son.

274
00:19:50,982 --> 00:19:52,566
Store's closed, mister.

275
00:19:52,650 --> 00:19:55,318
I'm not here for cigarettes
or bubble gum, my boy.

276
00:19:55,403 --> 00:19:56,695
Can you tell me
the name of the person

277
00:19:56,779 --> 00:19:58,446
who broke the record
on that game over there?

278
00:19:58,531 --> 00:20:00,448
Where I might find him?

279
00:20:01,993 --> 00:20:04,953
Alex Rogan.
You're looking at him.

280
00:20:05,663 --> 00:20:08,290
Alex Rogan. Aha!

281
00:20:09,041 --> 00:20:11,126
- Who are you?
- Centauri's the name.

282
00:20:11,210 --> 00:20:13,545
I invented Starfighter,
which is why I'm here.

283
00:20:13,629 --> 00:20:14,963
- It is?
- It is.

284
00:20:15,047 --> 00:20:17,591
We have to talk about a matter
of utmost importance.

285
00:20:17,675 --> 00:20:19,384
Step into my office.

286
00:20:19,468 --> 00:20:21,845
That's it. Come on now.

287
00:20:22,638 --> 00:20:24,598
Nothing to be afraid of.

288
00:20:29,562 --> 00:20:32,355
Oh, yes. Say hello
to my assistant, Beta.

289
00:20:33,274 --> 00:20:34,524
Howdy.

290
00:20:36,235 --> 00:20:37,360
Ow!

291
00:20:37,695 --> 00:20:40,822
I must congratulate
you on your virtuoso
performance, my boy.

292
00:20:40,907 --> 00:20:42,282
Centauri is impressed.

293
00:20:42,408 --> 00:20:43,783
I've seen them come
and I've seen them go.

294
00:20:43,868 --> 00:20:45,994
But you're the best, my boy.
Dazzling.

295
00:20:46,078 --> 00:20:48,079
Light years ahead
of the competition.

296
00:20:48,205 --> 00:20:50,248
Which is why
Centauri is here.

297
00:20:50,958 --> 00:20:52,918
He's got a little
proposition for you.

298
00:20:53,961 --> 00:20:55,170
Are you interested?

299
00:20:56,505 --> 00:20:57,839
(CHUCKLES)
I guess.

300
00:20:59,675 --> 00:21:00,842
