keep it for a surprise.

304
00:21:11,479 --> 00:21:15,148
Trust me. Oh, you're
gonna love it. Love it!

305
00:21:19,987 --> 00:21:21,237
(CHUCKLES)

306
00:21:21,447 --> 00:21:24,783
The amusing thing about this,
it's all a big mistake.

307
00:21:24,867 --> 00:21:26,451
That particular
Starfighter game

308
00:21:26,535 --> 00:21:28,453
was supposed to be
delivered to Vegas,

309
00:21:28,537 --> 00:21:30,455
not some flea-speck
trailer park

310
00:21:30,539 --> 00:21:32,499
in the middle of tumbleweeds
and tarantulas.

311
00:21:32,583 --> 00:21:35,585
So, it must be fate,
destiny, blind chance,

312
00:21:35,670 --> 00:21:37,420
luck, even,
that brings us together.

313
00:21:38,214 --> 00:21:41,299
And as the poet says,
"The rest is history."

314
00:21:45,221 --> 00:21:46,596
(BEEPING)

315
00:21:51,602 --> 00:21:53,979
Where are you going?
Where are you taking me?

316
00:21:54,063 --> 00:21:56,898
I told you. I wanna
save it for a surprise.

317
00:21:56,983 --> 00:22:01,820
