to tell you his tricks?

319
00:22:04,365 --> 00:22:06,950
Who sneaks downstairs to peek
at his Christmas presents?

320
00:22:07,034 --> 00:22:09,285
No. Of course you're not!

321
00:22:09,370 --> 00:22:12,163
