335
00:25:32,990 --> 00:25:34,115
(BEEPING)

336
00:25:49,298 --> 00:25:55,094
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

337
00:26:03,979 --> 00:26:06,189
(VOICE ON PA
SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

338
00:26:14,073 --> 00:26:16,658
