342
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:54,529
Hi! How are you?
What is this?

343
00:26:55,489 --> 00:26:57,824
Listen. Do you speak
English? I'd. . .

344
00:26:58,450 --> 00:26:59,993
This is nice but. . .

