just give him a ring.

353
00:27:20,639 --> 00:27:23,933
My stay?
What are you talking about?
Where are we?

354
00:27:24,018 --> 00:27:26,060
Welcome to Rylos, my boy!

355
00:27:27,146 --> 00:27:28,313
Rylos?

356
00:27:28,939 --> 00:27:31,274
Wait a minute. You mean. . .
You mean like in a game?

357
00:27:31,358 --> 00:27:33,318
Oh, he's quick.
He's quick. He's very quick.

358
00:27:33,402 --> 00:27:36,487
He's speechless.
So long, Alex! Have fun!

359
00:27:36,572 --> 00:27:39,907
May the luck of
the Seven Pillars of Gulu
be with you at all times.

360
00:27:39,992 --> 00:27:43,494
Oh, someday these cheapskates
will thank Centauri. Trust me.

361
00:27:43,579 --> 00:27:44,746
(EXCLAIMS IN ALIEN DIALECT)

362
00:27:48,292 --> 00:27:50,209
Where the hell is June?

363
00:27:55,424 --> 00:27:57,675
Yolanda, baby!

364
00:27:58,427 --> 00:28:05,099
(GROANING)

365
00:28:08,437 --> 00:28:09,771
LOUIS: Hi, Maggs.

366
00:28:10,773 --> 00:28:12,106
Hi, Louis.

367
00:28:12,941 --> 00:28:14,067
Is he up?

368
00:28:14,151 --> 00:28:18,196
Yeah. He's been up
all night moaning.

369
00:28:23,035 --> 00:28:24,369
Alex?

370
00:28:28,415 --> 00:28:30,917
Your mother told me
